results.deck: Ganbarion is a Japanese videogame developer.
results.description:
Overview

Ganbarion Co., Ltd. is a video game development studio based in Fukuoka, Japan. The company has been in business since August 13th, 1999. Their most popular titles have been the Jump Stars series on the Nintendo DS, which includes Jump Superstars and Jump Ultimate Stars. They have also created a number of games based on the One Piece license. Most recently, the company developed their first original IP, Pandora's Tower, in collaboration with Nintendo.
